A look at the top scorers in the Premier League as Son Heung-min chases down Mohamed Salah in the race for the Golden Boot. Tottenham Hotspur's Heung-min finished first jointly with Liverpool's Moh Salah with 23 goals each. Cristiano Ronaldo lies in third place with 18 goals, with last year's Golden Boot winner Harry Kane in fourth with 17 goals. Sadio Mane was fifth with 16 goals while his team mate Diogo Jota was sixth with 15 goals.